WEBVTT

1
00:22:39.483 --> 00:22:42.785 
"Dear Mother,

2
00:22:42.787 --> 00:22:45.688 
记得你问我 当你病了时
remember, you asked me

3
00:22:45.690 --> 00:22:48.458 
when you were sick--

4
00:22:48.460 --> 00:22:50.993 
临死?
well, dying--?

5
00:22:50.995 --> 00:22:53.596 
那年是秋天．10月
It was fall.

6
00:22:53.598 --> 00:22:57.467 
October.

7
00:22:57.469 --> 00:23:01.371 
那年还很热．在你的房间
Still hot that year, and your room--

8
00:23:01.373 --> 00:23:04.507 
像有种腐烂的苹果香味
it smelled like sweet, rotten apples.

9
00:23:09.480 --> 00:23:13.950 
我用手把你抱在怀里
And I was holding your head in my arms

